{"tid":1741761,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"開始真係相信支持勇武抗爭同港獨既人係鬼","createTime":"2019-11-20T13:03:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-20T13:20:11.000Z","uid":31637,"like":1,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"2a1e0fc5495be14542298a65da1b74290b2fc788","tid":1741761,"uid":31637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T13:03:57.000Z","msg":"勇武抗爭, 係所有抗爭之中最撚高成本既抗爭, 同勇武革命完全唔同, 勇武抗爭係指以激進既手段增加政府管治成本, 完全冇打算推翻政權, 因為從來都冇打算至人於死地. 所以武器都係D殺傷力極低既野為主, 例如汽油彈<br />\n成本高, 殺傷力低,只適合打悲情牌<br />\n<br />\n港獨, 其實就係完全孤立香港<br />\n愛國不愛黨, 其實就係孤立共產黨<br />\n見美國呢排成撚日講,中共同中國完全冇關,我就知道美國就係想孤立共產黨<br />\n習近平就係靠打貪打港獨牢固自己權力, 本來冇港獨一物, 點解習近平上任之後就有港獨?<br />\n其實就係想以港獨取代民主自由等名詞, 方便團結14億人"},{"pid":"039c48c56aef24eed3345535b5bcc5af5d33d00e","tid":1741761,"uid":167548,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T13:04:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>左膠退散圖<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n左膠見到藍絲有危險<br />\n再打會死！唔好再打！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TemFoaQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTemFoaQ.jpg&h=02bd1e1b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n左膠見到黑警有危險<br />\n包紮再護送到安全地方<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Qi4GR35.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQi4GR35.png&h=946db0f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dNAu0Xs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdNAu0Xs.png&h=5d2cd3e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n左膠見到政府建築物受破壞<br />\n以一擋萬<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hiCxemR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhiCxemR.jpg&h=eda17ebb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n左膠見到手足有危險<br />\n不了<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tvGBFXt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtvGBFXt.jpg&h=0487de6d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Axnxehu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA